stories.title: West Indies v Australia, Third One-Day Internatioal
Symonds and Clarke in charge as Aussies go three up
stories.summary: It was an unfamiliar-looking Australian side - no Adam Gilchrist, no Darren Lehmann, no Brett Lee (so no Lee in the Leeward Islands) - but by the end of this match, at the beautiful Beausejour Stadium in St Lucia, the tale was rather more familiar
